tod [SUBCOMMAND] [OPTIONS...]

... where SUBCOMMAND is one of:
	- help:    this help page

	- ls|list: list todo lines. Supported options:
		--format=editor for editor support
		--dir=PATH

	- mark:    mark todo as done
		--dir=PATH
		--save mark in place (defaults to dry run)
		--comment=COMMENT mark with COMMENT (ie. replace 'TODO' with 'Done (comment):')
		done - mark as 'Done' (default)
		none - Do not mark as done - scrub todo, or replace with comment (if supplied)
